# Frontend environment configuration
# For native development with Vite proxy:
# DO NOT set VITE_API_URL - leave it commented to use default /api/v1 proxy
# The Vite dev server will proxy /api requests to http://127.0.0.1:8000

# Port Normalization:
# Revert backend target to canonical development port 8000.
# Preferred patterns:
#   1. Native dev (backend on 8000, frontend on 5173): set explicit http://127.0.0.1:8000/api/v1
#   2. Fullstack Docker (backend serves SPA on 8080): set relative /api/v1 so same-origin works.
# Uncomment ONE of the lines below as needed.
VITE_API_URL=http://127.0.0.1:8000/api/v1
# VITE_API_URL=/api/v1
